  <name>InfluxDB Studio</name>
  <summary>InfluxDB database management and visualization tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      InfluxDB Studio is a modern desktop application for managing and visualizing InfluxDB time-series databases.
      It provides an intuitive interface for querying data, creating dashboards, and monitoring your time-series data.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Connect to InfluxDB instances</li>
      <li>Execute Flux and InfluxQL queries</li>
      <li>Visualize time-series data</li>
      <li>Manage databases and measurements</li>
      <li>Create and edit dashboards</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
